{"abstract":[{"text":"Computes accessibility contrast ratio between two colors in hexadecimal strings.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the hexadecimal strings are colors format in RGBA, will use their format in RGB (i.e. apply opacity, not truncate).","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"contrastRatios"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"lhs"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"rhs"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"One color to test"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"lhs"},{"name":"rhs","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Another color to test"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The computed ratio and flags saying if it match 3:1, 4.5:1 or 7:1","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See https:\/\/www.w3.org\/WAI\/WCAG21\/Techniques\/general\/G18.html#procedure"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/contrastratios(_:_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contrastRatios","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV14contrastRatiosyACSgSS_SStFZ","symbolKind":"method","title":"contrastRatios(_:_:)"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/contrastRatios(_:_:)"},"references":{"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"}],"url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","abstract":[{"text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is for example the case for France with the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"also named “RGAA”.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"role":"collection","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_layers.png"}],"title":"Foundations","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations"},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}],"